data.description: Welcome to your new home in the ultimate Smyrna location! Fox Chapel offers unparallelled walkability to Ivy Walk, St Benedicts, the Silver Comet Trail, West Village and more! It is close to I-285 and easy access to Vinings, the Battery, Buckhead and the Westside. This cul-de-sac home is stunning and has been meticulously maintained and upgraded, with designer paint colors, fixtures and finishes throughout. Gleaming hardwood floors and a grand 2-story foyer greet you, and you instantly know you are in for something special. Stained French doors lead to a sunny home office. The light-filled kitchen boasts beautiful cabinetry, an island, and a breakfast nook with built-in bench and bookshelves. A gorgeous and functional butler's pantry/scullery offers a wine fridge and tons of additional storage. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the dramatic 2-story fireside family room. A dining room offers two walls of windows for the ultimate entertaining experience. The brand new back deck overlooks the private, gorgeous backyard which is ideal for play or relaxation. Upstairs, you will find a gracious primary suite boasting a trey ceiling, a sitting area, and a renovated spa-like ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, an oversized glass shower, separate soaking tub, and a huge walk-in closet. Two spacious guestrooms share a full guest bathroom, and there is a laundry room upstairs. The full, finished Terrace Level offers a large great room and a kitchenette/bar with a kegerator and beverage fridge. The best place to watch games or movies! There is also a screened porch on this level - which is ideal for indoor/outdoor living. There is a fourth bedroom and a full bathroom on this level, private and ideal for guests. This home has been thoughtfully and lovingly upgraded and maintained. It shows like a model! Don't miss your chance to own this exquisite residence in an ideal Atlanta location.
